{
  "stem": "18626.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She would call the Germans, say, hey!",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here is a Jew there without a star.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you were taken and you were shot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were not rewarded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't say all Lithuanians did it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But comparing with other countries, they were expert of killing Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lithuania is known for not killing only the Lithuanish Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They begged the Germans gestapo-- and the gestapo to bring Jews from other countries and there have the pleasure to kill them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I've seen transport from Germany and from other countries, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the trucks, taken to the ninth ward and they were killed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Lithuanians had the biggest pleasures.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Germans were smoking the cigars and cigarettes, and the Lithuanians with the machine guns proudly finished up only not the Lithuanian Jews, but German Jews, and I think Hungarian Jews too.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think French Jews too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But German Jews I know for sure, because some of the clothing too fell off from the trucks, and Lithuanians find in the pockets, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Clothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of the clothing from the German Jews they'll send in in the ghetto, in magazines, to give out clothing for the Jews in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some Jews in the ghetto, Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LITHUANIAN], who was the chief, you know, in the clothing department, and in the-- in the department of the [GERMAN], was Mr.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LITHUANIAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He would-- he hesitated to release from that magazine the German clothes to the Lithuanian Jews, because it-- he didn't want, to, you know, the tragedy should become bigger.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was kept in locked magazines in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's what the Lithuanians did.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
